---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const profile = {
  name: "Vipin V Kartha",
  title: "Senior Backend Engineer",
  location: "Berlin, Germany",
  contact: {
    phone: "(+49) 1781723761",
    email: "vipinvkartha@gmail.com",
    linkedin: "https://linkedin.com/in/vipinvkartha",
    github: "https://github.com/vipinvkartha"
  },
  summary: `Senior Backend Engineer with 9+ years of expertise in building robust, scalable systems. Currently driving technical innovations at Babbel GmbH in Berlin.

As a polyglot developer proficient in Golang, Node.js (TypeScript), Ruby on Rails, and C++, I bring:

• Deep expertise in microservice architecture and event-driven systems
• Proven track record in both fast-paced startups and established enterprises
• Strong focus on delivering maintainable, production-ready solutions
• Extensive experience with cloud infrastructure and distributed systems

My diverse background across different tech stacks and business environments has shaped me into an adaptable engineer who thrives on complex challenges and consistently delivers high-quality results.

I combine technical excellence with a pragmatic approach to problem-solving, ensuring that solutions are not just technically sound but also align with business objectives.`,
  skills: {
    programming: [
      { name: "Golang", level: 5 },
      { name: "Node.js", level: 4 },
      { name: "TypeScript", level: 4 },
      { name: "Ruby on Rails", level: 4 },
      { name: "C++", level: 3 }
    ],
    backend: [
      { name: "ElasticSearch", level: 4 },
      { name: "Kinesis", level: 4 },
      { name: "Express", level: 5 },
      { name: "REST API", level: 5 },
      { name: "GraphQL", level: 4 },
      { name: "TypeOrm", level: 4 },
      { name: "Firebase", level: 3 },
      { name: "MQTT", level: 3 }
    ],
    devops: [
      { name: "AWS (Lambda, SQS, Cloudwatch, SNS, ECS)", level: 4 },
